{"tid":519031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"古代人個種講 義氣既情懷 今時今日既人真係學唔到","createTime":"2018-01-04T02:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T11:25:15.000Z","uid":120070,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e10524bfd45f46d99d46bc03bc1f848d53a92fdb","tid":519031,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:56:01.000Z","msg":"古代人對義氣 個種氣魄 真係可以赴湯蹈火，輕則千里送鵝毛 重則上刀山為左義氣 斷隻手臂都無問題<br />\n個種情懷 同現代啲契弟真係無得比 <br />\n 所以難怪古代咁多將士 錯信於人 被計謀害死<br />\n <br />\n古人 真係信左你就信你  人類係個時 仲好善良其實 <br />\n  <br />\n呢家啲人 連連少少義氣 都真係無<br />\n 仲有幾多人 明白 &ldquo;義氣&rdquo; 兩個字<br />\n再發現 越有錢既人 越無義氣 成個腦淨係得 著數<br />\n&ldquo; 睬你都傻&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n現代人與人之間 既感情 真係越黎越可悲"},{"pid":"1ed6ee1c175f867cb4350343837518b298f3d1ba","tid":519031,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40b3c0bfacee705339eb2d7e1c5e2f0032164e7","tid":519031,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef08458d5c923cc8db48f39bc7f14837404e6fd6","tid":519031,"uid":41974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:20:37.000Z","msg":"今時今日嘅信任，只係流於表面，仲頂要係有利益關係前題下。"},{"pid":"34ea3c37f8134db8567901659562114b10dd6b3c","tid":519031,"uid":53794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:42:00.000Z","msg":"呢啲人已經淘汰咗 死曬"},{"pid":"4fd3249cb3adc44bbbd9b09833fec9c3e1a75cda","tid":519031,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34ea3c37f8134db8567901659562114b10dd6b3c","tid":519031,"uid":53794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:42:00.000Z","msg":"呢啲人已經淘汰咗 死曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T03:55:57.000Z","msg":"可想言之 呢家個社會 已經係幾咁 變壞<br />\n人類再咁落去就好似個 水塘 越黎越染污咁 翻唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"